<br>
&quot;I apologise that I am troubling you with all these questions about your warrior women.  I promise that this is my last one.  Are some Goddesses allowed to join a few of the Greek Amazon tribes?&quot;<br>
<br>
Her greyblue occulars fell one Artemis's face as she awaited her answer, pushing each thought about her husband in the cockroach form to the back of her head.<br>
